		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Color blindness</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about color deficiencies.  For the term describing activities undertaken and services provided without regard to the racial characteristics, see <a href="/wiki/Color_blindness_(race)" title="Color blindness (race)">Color blindness (race)</a>.  For the film, see <a href="/wiki/Colour_Blind_(2009_film)" title="Colour Blind (2009 film)">Colour Blind (2009 film)</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox" width="200" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 95%; text-align:left">
<tr>
<td style="text-align: center; background: lightgrey; font-size: 95%;" colspan="2"><b>Color blindness</b><br />
<i>Classification and external resources</i></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th><a href="/wiki/ICD" title="ICD" class="mw-redirect">ICD</a>-<a href="/wiki/List_of_ICD-10_codes" title="List of ICD-10 codes" class="mw-redirect">10</a></th>
