</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Rainbow_Protanopia.svg" class="image" title="The colors of the rainbow as viewed by a person with protanopia."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d4/Rainbow_Protanopia.svg/180px-Rainbow_Protanopia.svg.png" width="180" height="111" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
